#: ../../source/faq.md:1
msgid "FAQ & Troubleshooting"
msgstr "常见问题与故障排查"

#: ../../source/faq.md:3
msgid ""
"Common questions and fixes. If something here doesn't help, please [open an "
"issue](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/issues)."
msgstr ""
"常见问题及解决方法。若此处未能解决你的问题，请[提交 issue](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/issues)。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:5
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/faq.md:7
msgid "**Which Python versions are supported?**"
msgstr "**支持哪些 Python 版本？**"

#: ../../source/faq.md:9
msgid "Python 3.10 and newer."
msgstr "Python 3.10 及更高版本。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:11
msgid "**How do I enable the optional features?**"
msgstr "**如何启用可选功能？**"

#: ../../source/faq.md:13
msgid "Some features need extra dependencies:"
msgstr "部分功能需要额外依赖："

#: ../../source/faq.md:15
msgid "**Keyboard control** (`pynput`): `pip install ir-sim[keyboard]`"
msgstr "**键盘控制**（`pynput`）：`pip install ir-sim[keyboard]`"

#: ../../source/faq.md:16
msgid "**ORCA group behavior** (`pyrvo`): `pip install pyrvo`"
msgstr "**ORCA 群体行为**（`pyrvo`）：`pip install pyrvo`"

#: ../../source/faq.md:17
msgid ""
"**Saving videos** (`imageio[ffmpeg]`): included in `pip install ir-sim[all]`"
msgstr "**保存视频**（`imageio[ffmpeg]`）：包含在 `pip install ir-sim[all]` 中"

#: ../../source/faq.md:18
msgid "**Everything**: `pip install ir-sim[all]`"
msgstr "**全部功能**：`pip install ir-sim[all]`"

#: ../../source/faq.md:20
msgid "Display and rendering"
msgstr "显示与渲染"

#: ../../source/faq.md:22
msgid "**Can I run IR-SIM without a display (server / CI / notebook)?**"
msgstr "**能否在没有显示器的环境（服务器 / CI / notebook）中运行 IR-SIM？**"

#: ../../source/faq.md:24
msgid "Yes. Pass `display=False` to skip the interactive window:"
msgstr "可以。传入 `display=False` 即可跳过交互式窗口："

#: ../../source/faq.md:30
msgid ""
"On a fully headless machine (no display at all), also select a non-"
"interactive Matplotlib backend **before** importing IR-SIM:"
msgstr "在完全无显示的机器上（没有任何显示设备），还需在导入 IR-SIM **之前**选择非交互式的 Matplotlib 后端："

#: ../../source/faq.md:38
msgid ""
"or run the script under a virtual display: `xvfb-run python your_script.py`."
msgstr "或在虚拟显示下运行脚本：`xvfb-run python your_script.py`。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:40
msgid "**How do I make the simulation run faster?**"
msgstr "**如何让仿真运行得更快？**"

#: ../../source/faq.md:42
msgid ""
"Render less often than you step: increase `world.sample_time` relative to "
"`step_time`, render every N steps instead of every step, or disable "
"rendering entirely with `display=False` for batch runs."
msgstr ""
"让渲染频率低于步进频率：增大 `world.sample_time`（相对于 `step_time`），每 N "
"步渲染一次而非每步都渲染，或在批量运行时用 `display=False` 完全关闭渲染。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:44
msgid "Saving animations"
msgstr "保存动画"

#: ../../source/faq.md:46
msgid "**How do I export a GIF or video?**"
msgstr "**如何导出 GIF 或视频？**"

#: ../../source/faq.md:48
msgid ""
"Set `save_ani=True` in `make()` and call `env.end()` to write the file:"
msgstr "在 `make()` 中设置 `save_ani=True`，并调用 `env.end()` 写出文件："

#: ../../source/faq.md:60
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"GIF export works out of the box. **Video (`.mp4`) requires ffmpeg** — "
"install it with `pip install imageio[ffmpeg]` (or `pip install ir-"
"sim[all]`). See {doc}`Render and Save Animation <usage/save_animation>`."
msgstr ""
"GIF 导出开箱即用。**视频（`.mp4`）需要 ffmpeg** —— 通过 `pip install imageio[ffmpeg]`（或 "
"`pip install ir-sim[all]`）安装。参见 {doc}`渲染与保存动画 <usage/save_animation>`。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:62
msgid "Reproducibility"
msgstr "可复现性"

#: ../../source/faq.md:64
msgid "**How do I get reproducible random scenes?**"
msgstr "**如何获得可复现的随机场景？**"

#: ../../source/faq.md:66
msgid "Seed IR-SIM's RNG, either through `make()` or `set_seed`:"
msgstr "为 IR-SIM 的随机数生成器设置种子，可通过 `make()` 或 `set_seed`："

#: ../../source/faq.md:77
msgid ""
"All built-in randomness (random distributions, random shape generators) "
"routes through this RNG. Custom code using `numpy.random` or Python's "
"`random` should be seeded separately, or switched to IR-SIM's RNG."
msgstr ""
"所有内置随机性（随机分布、随机形状生成器）都经由该随机数生成器。使用 `numpy.random` 或 Python `random` "
"的自定义代码应单独设种，或改用 IR-SIM 的随机数生成器。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:79
msgid "Common errors"
msgstr "常见错误"

#: ../../source/faq.md:81
msgid ""
"**`ModuleNotFoundError: pynput`** — Keyboard control needs `pynput`: `pip "
"install ir-sim[keyboard]`."
msgstr ""
"**`ModuleNotFoundError: pynput`** —— 键盘控制需要 `pynput`：`pip install ir-"
"sim[keyboard]`。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:83
msgid ""
"**`ModuleNotFoundError: pyrvo`** — The ORCA group behavior needs `pyrvo`: "
"`pip install pyrvo`."
msgstr ""
"**`ModuleNotFoundError: pyrvo`** —— ORCA 群体行为需要 `pyrvo`：`pip install pyrvo`。"

#: ../../source/faq.md:85
msgid ""
"**Saving a video produces nothing** — `ffmpeg` is missing. Install it with "
"`pip install imageio[ffmpeg]`. GIF export does not need ffmpeg."
msgstr ""
"**保存视频没有任何输出** —— 缺少 `ffmpeg`。通过 `pip install imageio[ffmpeg]` 安装。GIF 导出不需要 "
"ffmpeg。"
